com.acs.audiojack

Class TrackData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acs.audiojack.TrackData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AesTrackData, DukptTrackData

    public abstract class TrackData
extends java.lang.Object
    The TrackData class represents the track data after swiping a card from the reader.
